{"tid":1721173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「實用分析」大家要記住綠甲甴追捕既pattern","createTime":"2019-11-14T14:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T15:38:41.000Z","uid":198684,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8f22f2a55c171fd7bfbd87e4a35a4cefffcd7901","tid":1721173,"uid":198684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:54:17.000Z","msg":"班green object分三更<br />\n中更同夜更交接時間大約係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">22:30-23:15</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">通常</span></span>如果雙方對峙，未到交更時佢哋會保留體力，鳩射下煙射下彈咁。<br />\n而長跑大追捕會係臨交更做（因為可以chur盡佢）<br />\n捉到就捉，捉唔到就尻捉交數<br />\n<br />\n其次就係交更後果批一落地(夜晚居多）會黎次大追捕驅散，因為唔想拖太夜<br />\n<br />\n所以夜晚如果開花到咗<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">22:30-23:15</span></span>依段時間記住記住打醒精神！ 保持翻安全距離！<br />\n<br />\n以上分析地區開花既<span style=\"color: green;\">綠甲甴</span>適用"},{"pid":"2aab2058325e555300027f26dd514e6cede80907","tid":1721173,"uid":6942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:55:13.000Z","msg":"幫推!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46fcec94ec8e239f1da82f73a8349344708fad3e","tid":1721173,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:55:25.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1a74ee2549638fdd189e49af60fae231f76c76f0","tid":1721173,"uid":198684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:57:08.000Z","msg":"留意翻好多被<span style=\"color: red;\">追捕</span>既都係臨近交更/交更後<br />\n<br />\n有其他見解手足可以一齊討論下啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a0f52a562a47a53cea623a0b26d75c5f70f1f3","tid":1721173,"uid":219265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:01:35.000Z","msg":"所以先會話入夜就危險"},{"pid"